    summary: "The value of mining and panning output rose 23% to over US$1 billion in 2025, about a fifth of GDP and the single biggest driver of last year's growth. The sector's rise brings export earnings and revenue — and a deepening concentration of the economy's fortunes.",
    source: 'TrueRate',
    date: '2026-04-01',
